## Retrieve a storage


> Example Request

```bash
curl -X GET \
  <%= config[:endpoint] %>/api/public/v3/media/storage?id=cd003123-7ec9-4f3a-9d7c-f2de93e83e49 \
  -H 'Authorization: <%= config[:token] %>' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
```

